<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333333;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
      }
      .container {
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 30px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      .header {
        color: #2c3e50;
        text-align: center;
        border-bottom: 2px solid #f1f1f1;
        padding-bottom: 20px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .otp-display {
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        border: 1px dashed #3498db;
        padding: 15px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 28px;
        letter-spacing: 5px;
        margin: 25px 0;
        color: #e74c3c;
        font-weight: bold;
        border-radius: 5px;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 30px;
        padding-top: 20px;
        border-top: 2px solid #f1f1f1;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #7f8c8d;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .warning {
        background-color: #fff8e1;
        padding: 10px 15px;
        border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
        margin: 20px 0;
        font-size: 14px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h2 style="margin: 0; color: #3498db">Hello <%= name %>,</h2>
        <p style="margin: 5px 0 0">Here's your One-Time Password</p>
      </div>

      <p>Please use the following OTP to complete your verification:</p>

      <div class="otp-display"><%= otp %></div>

      <div class="warning">
        ⚠️ <strong>Important:</strong> This OTP is valid for 10 minutes only. Do
        not share it with anyone.
      </div>

      <p>
        If you didn't request this OTP, please ignore this email or contact our
        support team immediately.
      </p>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>Thank you for choosing our service!</p>
        <p>© 2023 Your Company Name. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
